  "tcmTraditionalUsage": {
    "en": "Barley is sweet and has a neutral taste, affecting the liver, spleen and stomach meridians. It is prepared from germinated barley seed which has been soaked in water. Medicinally, it is used to invigorate the stomach and treat bloating of the abdomen due to stagnation of food. It strengthens the stomach generally and facilitates the smooth flow of liver chi. Large amounts also have an inhibitory effect on lactation in breastfeeding women.\n",
    "zh-Hant": "炒麥芽是消食藥，味甘，藥性平，歸脾、胃、肝經，能消食健胃，疏肝消脹，常用於食滯或肝鬱引起的腹脹不適。\n",
    "zh-Hans": "炒麥芽是消食药，味甘，药性平，歸脾、胃、肝经，能消食健胃，疏肝消脹，常用于食滯或肝郁引起的腹脹不適。\n"
  },
